highlights.text: Linkin Park has the most spots on Top Songs Germany. “The Emptiness Machine” is the highest at #20.
“Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Germany the longest, at 334 days straight.
“Gianna - Harris & Ford x BIG TIM Remix” by Pietro Basile, Harris & Ford, and BIG TIM is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Germany, up 31 spots at #153.
